{"data":[{"date":"09:30 30/07","title":"Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Leicester City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai ng\u00f4i sao ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Leicester City \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u0103m tia <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Maguire</span> v\u00e0 Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leicester kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire v\u00e0 Schmeichel cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi Chelsea, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c chia tay Thibaut Courtois v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Schmeichel s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u trong khung g\u1ed7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui t\u1eeb Leicester City khi HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 h\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ea3 Kasper v\u00e0 Harry \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c tr\u1ee5c x\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed1c s\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra gi\u00e1 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nTheo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, CLB Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1797","checkdouble":"192295"},{"date":"10:04 30/07","title":"HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec5n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup sang Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-barca-len-tieng-bo-ngo-kha-nang-tien-mina-sang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yerry Mina c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Anh, Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Mina x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n \u1edf Camp Nou sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra s\u00e2n. Kh\u00f4ng, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palmeiras l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-barca-len-tieng-bo-ngo-kha-nang-tien-mina-sang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u00e1n Mina cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t th\u00f4i. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. T\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e1n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Mina, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n cho Man Utd, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Harry Maguire hay Toby Alderweireld. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to \u0111\u1ebfn 1m94 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong tranh ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn h\u1eb3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca-180-191127.html\">Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e1\u201d kh\u1ecfi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/man-united-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-nguoi-thua-cua-barca-187-192031.html\">Man United b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span>\u00a0</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1796","checkdouble":"192296"},{"date":"10:10 30/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Petr Cech","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tan-binh-19-trieu-bang-len-tieng-canh-bao-petr-cech.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 30/7(V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Nga 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Ufa-vs-Lokomotiv-Moscow.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede ngay v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Lokomotiv Moscow n\u00ean k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Ufa c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thua t\u1edbi 5. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Ufa c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Domzale (Slovenia) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 Europa League. L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Ufa ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Lokomotiv Moscow kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 sau 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Nga, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Yuri Semin c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, Lokomotiv Moscow \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Neftyanik khi 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y th\u1ea5p khi m\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n* 11 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1eeba qua, Ufa th\u1eafng 4, Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 5, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2<br>\r\n* Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ufa<br>\r\n* 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc , Ufa \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lokomotiv Moscow<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nUfa: Yerkebulan Seidakhmet kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Vyacheslav Krotov ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow: C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1795","checkdouble":"192297"},{"date":"10:33 30/07","title":"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 IC Cup sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, Man Utd g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o. &quot;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a Club America, San Jose Earthquakes v\u00e0 AC Milan (kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u). M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-4.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, Jose Mourinho h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u0169i d\u00f9i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00eda. &quot;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&quot; ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool, t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9,...<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Man Utd vs Liverpool, s\u00e2n Michigan \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ebfn 101.254 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i (37.776, 32.549 v\u00e0 21.742). \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u01a1n, Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd: &quot;B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 xem nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u00e9, t\u00f4i xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u1edbi Inter Milan tr\u00ean TV&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t v\u1eafng. C\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 h\u1ecd y\u00eau. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Ander Herrera v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 g\u1eb7p Real Madrid (7h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8) v\u00e0 Bayern Munich (1h15 ng\u00e0y 6/8).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup-172-192295.html\">Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/luke-shaw-tiet-lo-su-that-ve-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-172-192210.html\">Luke Shaw ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-icc-2018-dem-nay-372-192208.html\">MU 1-4 Liverpool: Shaqiri ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, The Klopp b\u1eafn tan x\u00e1c b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-man-utd-bi-ghet-nhat-trong-so-cac-doi-bong-o-premier-league-172-192172.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Man Utd b\u1ecb gh\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-liverpool-tin-mu-se-khong-vao-noi-top-4-mua-giai-nay-172-192118.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool tin MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o n\u1ed5i top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-an-dinh-so-ao-cho-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-192109.html\">Man Utd \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o cho t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1794","checkdouble":"192298"},{"date":"10:15 30/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-3007.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 30/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-3007-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Digne s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf sao ng\u1ed7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Rabiot, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a PSG. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Blaugrana s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecfi mua Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ph\u00eda M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes c\u1ee7a Barca. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-3007-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ousmane Dembele r\u1eddi Camp Nou</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-192253.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-192253.html\">HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</span><br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal thay Rabiot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Ousmane Dembele \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song Arsenal v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n Dembele m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, n\u1ebfu anh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca chot tuong lai Vermaelen\" title=\"Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Vermaelen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 Thomas Vermaelen ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Domingos Quina c\u1ee7a West Ham. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang London \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1793","checkdouble":"192299"},{"date":"10:44 30/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 30/7 (V\u0110QG Nga 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/nhan-dinh-ufa-vs-lokomotiv-moscow-22h00-ngay-307-vdqg-nga-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 30/7(V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Nga 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow 22h00 ng\u00e0y 307 V\u0110QG Nga 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Ufa-vs-Lokomotiv-Moscow.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Ufa vs Lokomotiv Moscow: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede ngay v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Lokomotiv Moscow n\u00ean k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Ufa c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ufa \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thua t\u1edbi 5. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Ufa c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Domzale (Slovenia) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 Europa League. L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Ufa ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Lokomotiv Moscow kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 sau 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Nga, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Yuri Semin c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, Lokomotiv Moscow \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Neftyanik khi 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y th\u1ea5p khi m\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n* 11 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1eeba qua, Ufa th\u1eafng 4, Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 5, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2<br>\r\n* Lokomotiv Moscow th\u1eafng 2/3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ufa<br>\r\n* 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc , Ufa \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lokomotiv Moscow<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nUfa: Yerkebulan Seidakhmet kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Vyacheslav Krotov ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\nLokomotiv Moscow: C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1792","checkdouble":"192301"},{"date":"11:02 30/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: M.U chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/ngay-hom-nay-307.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (30/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 307, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 307, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/mu-muon-vuot-mat-everton-vu-yerry-mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nV\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Tony Alderweireld, HLV Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng bu\u00f4ng 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n - Yerry Mina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, Mina v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, anh c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c pha lao l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, v\u1edbi 3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Ba Lan, Senegal v\u00e0 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Mina \u1edf Nou Camp kh\u00e1 m\u1edd m\u1ecbt. Anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 trong vai tr\u00f2 trung v\u1ec7, sau Pique, Umtiti v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Lenglet.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi v\u1eady, Mina \u0111ang nh\u1ea5p nh\u1ed5m ra \u0111i. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, Barca ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 10,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 CLB, nh\u01b0ng nay h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu l\u1ea1i h\u01a1n g\u1ea5p 3 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Mina.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mina-len-35-trieu-bang-172-192242.html\">MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Real h\u1ecfi mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Chelsea gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 307 MU chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 307 MU chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-307-MU-chi-35-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-Barca--hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLos Blancos t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Courtois. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u di\u1ebfm mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i d\u00e0nh cho Keylor Navas v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m tr\u00ean h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Willian m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Real. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Barca cho ph\u00e9p Lucas Digne v\u1ec1 Everton</h2>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u00e3 ra th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean Lucas Digne r\u1eddi CLB. Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd mua Digne v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Digne kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Barca v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-180-192286.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Pulisic</h2>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9, Christian Pulisic \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i g\u1eaft gao. D\u00f9 v\u1eady trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pulisic lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri.\r\n<h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 sao Juventus</h2>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Mail, Man City \u0111ang t\u00ednh chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m trong di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e2n binh Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man xanh v\u1eeba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alex-sandro-dong-y-sang-psg-thay-vi-mu-172-191446.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PSG b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh Alex Sandro</h2>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Alex Sandro l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU trong su\u1ed1t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Tuy v\u1eady, hi\u1ec7n MU \u0111ang d\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c PSG gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua n\u00e0y. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 Alex Sandro l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1ea5y.\r\n<h2>Bayern Munich t\u00ednh k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t bom t\u1ea5n</h2>\r\nHLV Niko Kovac \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Allianz Arena m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Julian Draxler. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Werder Bremen n\u00e0y \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i PSG v\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Bayern c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro, b\u1edfi PSG cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n Draxler \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1791","checkdouble":"192302"},{"date":"11:21 30/07","title":"Fosu-Mensah t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/fosumensah-tu-tin-canh-tranh-vi-tri-o-mu-mua-toi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Fosu-Mensah t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Mourinho m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fosu-Mensah quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fosu-Mensah t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fosu-Mensah t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU m\u00f9a t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/fosumensah-tu-tin-canh-tranh-vi-tri-o-mu-mua-toi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fosu-Mensah t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man United cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm khi thi\u1ebfu \u0111i h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Chris Smalling, Antonio Valencia, Marcos Rojo, Diogo Dalot, Luke Shaw hay Eric Bailly.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 c\u0169ng c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111i c\u1ee7a Mourinho nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Victor Lindelof, Phil Jones v\u00e0 Ashley Young. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nh\u01b0 Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Jesse Lingard, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\"N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Crystal Palace. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. T\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 xem m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i, trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 trong vai tr\u00f2 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1eady n\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed duy nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i b\u1eaft g\u00f4n th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7\".</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fosu-Mensah t\u1ecf r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fosu-Mensah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i Michigan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Tuanzebe, Darmian v\u00e0 Bailly t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\"T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u00e0y qua ng\u00e0y. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu HLV c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tri\u1ec3n khai m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Real Madrid. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ch\u00fa \u00fd lcus n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady gi\u00fap \u00edch cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\".</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-307-187-192302.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: M.U chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-va-chelsea-nhan-tin-buon-ve-hang-hot-world-cup-172-192295.html\">Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1790","checkdouble":"192303"},{"date":"11:58 30/07","title":"MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/mu-don-sieu-bao-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-real.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang m\u1ea5t 17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ander Herrera v\u00e0 Eric Bailly \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Man United t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 g\u1eb7p Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. 8 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c th\u00ec \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u00ec h\u1ecd m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mu-don-sieu-bao-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-real.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU d\u00ednh b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNemanja Matic \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi sau ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 HLV Mourinho th\u00ec c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb3ng r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat 101.254 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Big House. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n khuy\u00ean c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1edbi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 Real s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u khi\u1ebfn ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i ICC v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi Man United tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 xem hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Inter tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i r\u1ea5t tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ph\u00e2n n\u1eeda c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7n binh th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 30% \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"V\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 4 hay 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 hy sinh h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec h\u1ecd quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi CLB. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0o hi\u1ec3m nguy v\u00ec h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec? Ch\u1eb3ng g\u00ec c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7\".<br>\r\n</em><em><br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda cho MU</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, HLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t an tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1edfi tranh sau \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 2 tu\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1edbm quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Matic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau World Cup, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00ec c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u1eeb World Cup. Valencia th\u00ec t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u00f2n sau khi \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ee9a con ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Martial ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\"V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Juan Mata ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ph\u00fat trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 th\u00ec n\u00ean quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nan gi\u1ea3i\".</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-307-187-192302.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: M.U chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau-172-192298.html\">Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1789","checkdouble":"192304"},{"date":"11:51 30/07","title":"C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u201cdanh s\u00e1ch \u0111en\u201d c\u1ee7a Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/22/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dimitar Berbatov v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Anthony Martial v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n \u1edf Old Trafford n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u00f4i m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man Utd n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Anthony Martial. V\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Old Trafford, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i MU 1-4 Liverpool m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Martial trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn qu\u1edf tr\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n con trai m\u1edbi ra \u0111\u1eddi l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Monaco v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t l\u00e2u h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Berbatov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Martial v\u00e0 Rashford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Berbatov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Martial v\u00e0 Rashford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/MU-muon-mua-Douglas-Costa-trong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Berbatov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Martial v\u00e0 Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Rashford c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang s\u1eafm vai k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Rashford \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi, tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Dimitar Berbatov m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0o hai h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi n\u1eb1m trong \u201cdanh s\u00e1ch \u0111en\u201d c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bulgaria:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Rashford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, c\u1ea3 Martial c\u0169ng v\u1eady. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u00ec hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f3 tin. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i. Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft kh\u00e1c, v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Martial v\u00e0 Rashford s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 MU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho\u2026 Martial</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1eafng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1788","checkdouble":"192306"},{"date":"07:04 30/07","title":"Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 5 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a qua, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chia tay CLB. Sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Juventus b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y minh ch\u1ee9ng cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Cristiano-Ronaldo-tro-lai-Juventus-tap-luyen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 n\u0103m qua, Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A song kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Bianconeri l\u00e0 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau 22 n\u0103m v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u00f4m qua, Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. H\u1eadu World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p th\u00eam ng\u00e0y ph\u00e9p v\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cristiano ronaldo\" title=\"cristiano ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Benfica, cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan t\u1eeb d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 MLS v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Paulo Dybala, Douglas Costa, Rodrigo Bentancur, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca, Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong phi\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bld-mu-ngan-can-mourinho-chieu-mo-sandro-172-192120.html\">BL\u0110 MU ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/xac-dinh-doi-thu-dau-tien-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-tren-dat-y-176-192108.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1787","checkdouble":"192282"},{"date":"07:31 30/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/chelsea-sap-vo-mong-chieu-mo-tuyen-thu-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;h\u00e0ng hot&rdquo;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Jordan Pickford b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd khi m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong khung th\u00e0nh Tam s\u01b0, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup, Pickford nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u1eefng Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Jordan-Pickford-sap-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Chelsea khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u01a1 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sunday Times m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Bayern v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng. Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"jordan pickford\" title=\"jordan pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jordan-pickford-cua-Everton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Everton b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland. Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n, Everton c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gia t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Pickford v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Everton tham gia v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League v\u1edbi Wolves ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-muon-roi-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-192252.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud-172-192243.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chelsea-bat-ngo-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-cua-arsenal-187-192241.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1786","checkdouble":"192283"},{"date":"07:58 30/07","title":"Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern: PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Boateng. </strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Silva. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U.</strong> Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft Napoli \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Manchester United cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Matteo Darmian. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n sau 2 n\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. </strong>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan mu\u1ed1n l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng thua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh. </strong>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Simeone thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Vrsaljko \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. </strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. HLV Diego Simeone hy v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" title=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/sao-atletico-madrid-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-khoac-ao-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Vrsaljko trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 sao tr\u1ebb ra \u0111i. </strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Rosenborg cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pedro Chirivella. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Bale.</strong> Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho hay Spurs kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua Ojo c\u1ee7a Liverpool. </strong>Middlesbrough \u0111ang m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sheyi Ojo t\u1eeb Liverpool. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Fulham m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t. Ngo\u00e0i Boro, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nottingham Forest c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd Ojo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1785","checkdouble":"192284"},{"date":"08:16 30/07","title":"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-harry-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Vuot-mat-MU,-Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Harry-Maguire-hinh-anh.jpg\"><br>\r\n            \u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maguire \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Maguire s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/MU-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-muc-tieu-65-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Harry Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Sergio Ramos. Los Blancos c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1eeb 60 \u0111\u1ebfn 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Maguire th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Leicester \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n, Maguire s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1784","checkdouble":"192285"},{"date":"08:31 30/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Digne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Alba, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca. 2 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Xac-nhan-Lucas-Digne-roi-Barca-cap-ben-Everton-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Digne kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb HLV Ernesto Valverde, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Lucas Digne \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Barca c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, song vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Digne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Digne, trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca xac nhan Digne cap ben Everton\" title=\"Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton </span>\u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia v\u00e0 Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Digne v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 xin ph\u00e9p Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDigne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 4. \u1ede s\u00e2n Goodison Park, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Leighton Baines.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Digne s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Everton d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Marco Silva, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng chia tay Wayne Rooney v\u00e0 Ramiro Funes Mori.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1783","checkdouble":"192286"}]}